TITLE: Numeric Array Summation Using Arrow Type Predicates
DESCRIPTION: Template function that sums values in any numeric (integer or float) Arrow array using type predicates.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/main/docs/source/cpp/datatypes.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: cpp
CODE:
```
template <typename ArrayType, typename DataType = typename ArrayType::TypeClass,
          typename CType = typename DataType::c_type>
arrow::enable_if_number<DataType, CType> SumArray(const ArrayType& array) {
  CType sum = 0;
  for (std::optional<CType> value : array) {
    if (value.has_value()) {
      sum += value.value();
    }
  }
  return sum;
}
```

