TITLE: Creating an ArrowSchema PyCapsule in C
DESCRIPTION: This C code demonstrates how to create a PyCapsule for an `ArrowSchema`. It allocates memory for the schema, fills in the fields (indicated by comments), and then creates a PyCapsule with a destructor function (`ReleaseArrowSchemaPyCapsule`) to release the memory when the capsule is no longer needed.  The capsule name is "arrow_schema".
