TITLE: Updating Arrow format flatbuffers generated code
DESCRIPTION: This shell script demonstrates how to update the Arrow format flatbuffers generated code. It includes steps for modifying flatbuffers schemas, generating TypeScript source, and cleaning up temporary files.
