TITLE: Hash Table First Pass Resize Algorithm
DESCRIPTION: Algorithm for the first pass of hash table resizing that handles non-overflow entries. It distributes entries from source block L to target blocks (2*L+0) and (2*L+1) based on the highest bit of the stamp.
