TITLE: Defining Arrow Acero Benchmark Function in CMake
DESCRIPTION: Creates a function to add Arrow Acero benchmarks with proper linking and labels. This function configures benchmarks with appropriate prefixes, labels, and dependencies, similar to the test function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/main/cpp/src/arrow/acero/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-16_snippet_2

